snippet: The racehorse Native Diver was exhumed from Hollywood Park and will be moved to a new resting place in California.
abstract: Racehorse Native Diver is exhumed from Hollywood Park and will be moved to a new resting place in California; grandson of horse's owner and breeder says he could not bear thought of the thoroughbred’s remains staying where they were as Hollywood Park is torn down.
lead_paragraph: The racehorse Native Diver was exhumed from Hollywood Park and will be moved to a new resting place in California.
